summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North and East Sixty-fifth Street from East Green Lake Boulevard to Latona Avenue et al in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing same under Ordinance No. 15794, creating Local Improvement District No. 1473 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
